            <img src="/images/mai.jpg" alt="Mai Minakami" class="rounded-xl">
        </figure>

        <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300">
            Salutations! I’m a Full-Stack Developer that transmute a piece of nothing 
            into a piece of something.
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300">
            In my free time I watch animes and listen a bit of music.
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300">
            If you would like to contact me about an opportunity or to share experiences, 
            please feel free to do so.
        </p>

        <ul class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 sm:flex-nowrap">
            <li>
                <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/caiocamargo007" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline underline-offset-2 text-purple-800 dark:text-purple-300">
                    LinkedIn
                </a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="https://github.com/SadS4ndWiCh" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline underline-offset-2 text-purple-800 dark:text-purple-300">
